{"tid":2199150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"私人檢控郭偉强案 律政司申再拖6周  慢必警告：倘放生勢眾籌覆核","createTime":"2020-09-12T03:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T03:21:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e3586f933c7ceb5242747ed9d2bcb33456e43a03","tid":2199150,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T03:20:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200912/TYKPDUWZGBFMVF6PNS6UJPFH2Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200912%2FTYKPDUWZGBFMVF6PNS6UJPFH2Q%2F&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=d4e7ff01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200912%2FTYKPDUWZGBFMVF6PNS6UJPFH2Q%2F&h=1db79bf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200912/TYKPDUWZGBFMVF6PNS6UJPFH2Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n私人檢控郭偉强案 律政司申再拖6周 <br />\n慢必警告：倘放生勢眾籌覆核<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3XotcQknWpQ18je64QVFruLjJsE=/937x691/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BF5NY6VBFJCRHJFKIP6BRXDIDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3XotcQknWpQ18je64QVFruLjJsE%3D%2F937x691%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBF5NY6VBFJCRHJFKIP6BRXDIDQ.jpg&h=9bf6682b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■今年5月立會內會選主席期間，工聯會郭偉强曾拉跌及拖行人民力量陳志全。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】人民力量陳志全就今年5月，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳志全昨表示收到律政司要求押後案件的通知。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他續指，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳志全聲言，如果律政司日後接管案件，向郭偉强撤控，他將會提出司法覆核，與政府打官司，推翻律政司撤控的決定，屆時他或要再次發起眾籌，因為上次他透過眾籌籌得的100萬元，只是針對向郭偉强提出私人檢控。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QJJ-naDYP3mZWpQdVdr1fZAmqbM=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3IQWQ26KCZBFZAD73F35DWVN3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQJJ-naDYP3mZWpQdVdr1fZAmqbM%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3IQWQ26KCZBFZAD73F35DWVN3Q.jpg&h=776cb596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n律政司長鄭若驊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n憂原告變被告<br />\n<br />\n他堅持為自己討回公道，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳志全指昨日收到法庭通知，指若在昨日下午4時前，沒有任何一方提出新的押後理由，便會如期於下周一兩時半於西九龍裁判法院提訊，但陳志全指，律政司隨時可以遲至下周一才向法庭陳情，提出押後的原因。此外，如今令陳志全擔心的是，自己有機會原告變被告，日後會被政府控以擾亂秩序：「律政司有乜醜事做唔出呢？其實我最驚唔係佢撤控，而係佢會告返我轉頭。」<br />\n<br />\n被告郭偉强則表示，。。。。"},{"pid":"370e92171c4f170d14ceaeb6be63fe319b504c7d","tid":2199150,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T03:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}